            "Jinan Metro Line 4 construction proceeds ahead of schedule.",
            "New policies introduced to support local agricultural startups.",
            "Cultural Heritage Center opens in Huaiyin District.",
            "Jinan ranks top 10 in national smart city index."
        ];

