Here is a complete, one-page HTML file containing the CSS and JavaScript required to create a functional (simulation) web scraping tool interface.

Since browser security policies (CORS) prevent a simple client-side HTML file from actually scraping arbitrary websites without a backend server, this application **simulates** the scraping process to demonstrate the UI/UX and logic flow requested.

